# Cursor Skill Router (Territory Developer)

When user request matches any trigger below:

1. Load the referenced skill file.
2. Follow all phases in order.
3. Keep scope minimal to that skill unless user asks broader work.

If a skill has Cursor-specific caveats, read `.cursor/rules/cursor-lifecycle-adapters.mdc`.

